	   <tr><td colspan=2>I have a lower level cleric that I have been playing when I need a break from my paladin, and I'm kind of at a loss. What is the best skill to learn for a cleric? I don't mean 1HB, Channel, or those. I mean blacksmithing, baking and so on.<br><br>I like to have at least one good skill, if only for roleplaying. My paladin is a great chef, and baking isn't too useful usually. ) So, what's a good skill for a high elf cleric?<br><br>Thanks!<br><br>&nbsp;<br>Valderessa Truesoul<br>Paladin, Heroine, and Healer of Rodcet Nife<br>Drinal Server</td></tr>
