	   <tr><td colspan=2>hmm...jewelry making blows for clerics, heh.  they can't enchant the metal themselves.  try and find a chanter to do it for you(unless you know one)you will be cutting into a chanters business.<br><br>tailoring is cool, good money to be made later on, not super money, but good.  and you can level against mobs that drop tailoring ingredients.  pretty cheap to be a tailor, as well.<br><br>you could also try blacksmithing, very expensive, and frankly, not worth it.<br><br>tailoring is good, try that.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
